    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks, that's a relief to hear. i was really worried it was my heart. it's just that the pressure is kinda intense and it's making me feel a bit lightheaded too. do you think i should take something for it? like maybe some of my usual anti-anxiety meds or something to help me just calm down and sleep it off?",
