      "content": "I understand the pressure and lightheadedness can be concerning, but it's crucial to stay calm and not self-medicate. If you're using anti-anxiety medication, make sure to take it as prescribed. If you're not already on medication, consider trying some relaxation techniques like deep breathing or meditation to help alleviate the symptoms. If the pressure and lightheadedness persist, it's best to consult a healthcare professional. Remember, I'm here to help you through this.",
